### 订单模块接口测试

### ========== 环境变量 ==========
### 请先通过登录接口获取Token，然后替换下方的token值
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ========== 1. 创建订单 ==========

### 创建订单 - 正常请求
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "张三",
  "telephone": "13800138000",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### 创建订单 - 另一个地址
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "李四",
  "telephone": "13900139000",
  "city": "上海",
  "address": "浦东新区陆家嘴100号"
}

### 创建订单 - 缺少收货人（应返回错误）
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "",
  "telephone": "13800138000",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### 创建订单 - 电话格式错误（应返回错误）
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "王五",
  "telephone": "12345",
  "city": "北京",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### 创建订单 - 缺少城市（应返回错误）
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "consignee": "赵六",
  "telephone": "13800138000",
  "city": "",
  "address": "朝阳路100号"
}

### ========== 2. 获取订单详情 ==========

### 获取订单详情 - 订单ID为1
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取订单详情 - 订单ID为2
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取订单详情 - 不存在的订单ID（应返回错误或空）
GET http://localhost:8080/orders/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========== 3. 下载订单发票 ==========

### 下载订单发票 - 订单ID为1
GET http://localhost:8080/invoice/download/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 下载订单发票 - 订单ID为2
GET http://localhost:8080/invoice/download/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
